  <div class="hero standard-restricted-width">
    {{ cohort_nav() }}
    <p class="hero__tag">
      You belong here
    </p>
    <h1 class="hero__title">
      Apply to be a entrepreneur at Ventures for Shared Prosperity
    </h1>
    <p class="hero__body g-max-4">
      With support from Wells Fargo we’re recruiting entrepreneurs to build 
      businesses to address the excess costs of poverty. We’re looking for 
      people that know if given the time, the money, and the audience, they can 
      channel their lived experiences, ideas, and talents into positive impact. 
